Robert Cusanelli of WHDH-TV was banned from the Bristol County courthouse after two jurors told the court they were followed by a van as they tried to get into their cars on Wednesday .
Two jurors informed the court Thursday morning that they saw someone watching them in a Ford Explorer as they made their way home in Boston .
The van was allegedly behind the jury bus as it headed towards an off-site parking lot where the jurors were dropped off at the end of the day .